<h1>#Personal Data</h1>
<h2>Personal Information</h2>
<p>We require members to provide some personal information (including, but not limited to, name, business address, contact information and depending on their profile, their driver&rsquo;s licence number and payment information) in order to create an account and begin interacting in our Marketplace.</p>
<p>Personal information collected by <em>Go99</em>&trade; and its service providers to manage accounts and process orders and related transactions. We do not disclose your personal information with third parties, except for disclosures required to process transactions through the App and as otherwise permitted by applicable law or as outlined in the Privacy Notice which can be found at www.<em>Go99</em>.ca/terms.</p>
<h2>Profile Information</h2>
<p>This data may include the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Personal name and contact details</li>
<li>Company name and contact details</li>
<li>Company GST and other industry relevant numbers</li>
<li>Driver&rsquo;s licence number is required for truck driver profiles</li>
