<p>Some examples of spam include:</p>
<ul>
<li>Unsolicited email offers sent to potential Members</li>
<li>Email messages sent to a member on a mailing list without that member's prior consent</li>
<li>Invitations to join a mailing list that aren't related to your <em>Go99</em>&trade; profile</li>
<li>Mail sent using <em>Go99</em>&trade; messages (or other App features) to send unsolicited commercial offers</li>
<li>Messages that include email addresses, phone numbers, or social media links, contact information or Member names relating to the App</li>
<li>Email and websites impersonating <em>Go99</em>&trade;</li>
</ul>
